Open Google & sign in with correct email id & password.
After login, Go in Google apps (9 dotted option) & click on Google Drive.
Click on New (+) button.
Then select google form option.
Create the google form by adding questions & options as per user convenience.
Go in "setting" Option which is at top.
Enable "Collect Email addresses" option to get all email add. from user.
Enable "limit responses to 1" Option by which user can fill the form only once.
Select "preview" option to make preview of created form.
